data.description: Contract Pending.  On market for backup offers only.  Step into comfort with this charming ranch in the Country Club neighborhood, where every detail is set for you to just move in and start living! Imagine stepping onto warm, heated marble floors in a beautifully remodeled bathroom, complete with a sleek vanity topped with quartz, easy-close drawers, and shower/tub wrapped in stylish tile. It doesn't stop there—enjoy recent upgrades like fresh paint, chic light fixtures, and stunning laminate floors in the dining space. Outside, the durable steel siding, private fenced yard, and prime location close to Nebraska Parkway, eateries, and shops add convenience to your lifestyle.
